                <note rend="inline" type="source">823.51/1550a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">White</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-05-16T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 16, 1944—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>513. For Rogers from Munro.<note n="58" xml:id="d1477fn58">Dana G. Munro,
                        President of the Foreign Bondholders Protective Council.</note> We agree
                    with you that proposal is totally unacceptable. We will cable about procedure
                    after further consultation with Department. [Munro.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
